  "text": "Fried et al. further validated GOALS as an assessment tool by demonstrating that it has concurrent validity by comparing GOALS scores with assessment of skills using a simulator [CITATION_1] . In 2007, Gumbs et al. demonstrated construct validity for GOALS for assessment of a complete laparoscopic cholecystectomy and laparoscopic appendectomy [CITATION_2] . This has added further evidence to the value and effectiveness of GOALS as a global assessment tool for laparoscopic skills.",
